Prerequisites
-------------
lz4 (de)compression libraries, from https://github.com/Cyan4973/lz4.
  On OS X, also available using "brew install lz4".
boost includes and libraries, from http://www.boost.org.
  On OS X, also available using "brew install boost".
google hash, from https://github.com/sparsehash/sparsehash.
  On OS X, also available using "brew install google-sparsehash".

Compiling vlog
--------------

- copy a suitable makefile.platform from the makefile.platform.examples
  directory (either the linux one or the OS X one).
- edit makefile.platform to your needs.
- run "make".
